items.name: Alice Alpaca
items.definition: Nestled in soft, huggable fur, this adorable stuffed animal features big, round eyes that sparkle with innocence, capturing hearts at first glance.

items.name: Lilly Lama
items.definition: With a charming stitched smile and plush, cuddly body, this sweet stuffed animal is the perfect companion for cozy bedtime hugs and imaginative play.

items.name: Cody Cow
items.definition: Its fuzzy ears perk up inquisitively, adding an extra touch of charm to this endearing stuffed creature, making it irresistibly cute and delightful.

items.name: Gwen Goose
items.definition: The gentle squishiness of its plush form invites tender squeezes, turning it into a cherished friend that brings warmth and comfort to all who embrace it.

items.name: Dotty Lama
items.definition: Sporting a playful demeanor, this little stuffed buddy boasts a whimsical expression that invites joy and companionship, making it impossible to resist its charm.

items.name: Chunky Monkey
items.definition: Adorned with a tiny bow and fuzzy paws, this lovable stuffed animal radiates sweetness, becoming a delightful confidant for both laughter-filled adventures and quiet moments of comfort.

items.name: Mr. Hooter Owl
items.definition: Its petite size and soft, pastel-colored fur make this endearing plush creature a perfect snuggle buddy, bringing a touch of enchantment to every cuddle session.

items.name: Joey Turkey
items.definition: With a velvety touch and an enchanting expression, this lovable stuffed companion is a heartwarming reminder that even the smallest cuddles can bring immense joy.

items.name: Zorro Zebra
items.definition: Go on adventures with the cute, cuddly and friendly Zebra. It will take you on the best adventures.
